<BaseLayout title="List of patent cases by Dr. Lavian - Dr. Tal Lavian">
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <h1>Cases - Expert Witness Testimony</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-with-sidebar">
      <div class="content-main">
        <p>Dr. Lavian is an expert in network communications and telecommunications. He has provided expert witness testimony in patent cases involving over 140 patents, written expert reports, and testified in over 80 depositions. He has testified in Federal courts, before judges and juries, USPTO PTAB IPR, and the ITC. In addition to his expertise in patent cases, Dr. Lavian provides expert testimony and litigation support services in network communications and telecommunications.</p>

        <p>He has testified in various courts, including the United States District Court, the United States Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO), the International Trade Commission (ITC), and other courts in the United States and Canada. He has also served as an expert witness in USPTO PTAB proceedings, including Inter partes reviews (IPRs), Covered Business Method (CBM) reviews, Post Grant Reviews (PGRs), Ex-Parte Re-Examinations, and PTO Interferences.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian is skilled in providing technical education for claim constructions and Markman hearings and is experienced in writing expert reports that include analyses, claim term definitions, and claim construction. He has a talent for making complex technical information accessible to audiences with varying technical expertise. He has provided product and technical analyses on patent portfolios, claim charts, prior art investigations, and patentability research.</p>

        <p>These cases involved leading companies, including Amazon, LinkedIn, Avaya, Netflix, T-Mobile, ZTE, AT&T, Ericsson, Sprint, Cisco Systems, Juniper Networks, Polycom, Motorola, HP, LG, WhatsApp, Instagram, Microsoft, Google, Huawei, Facebook, Samsung, and Apple.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.5rem;">Telecommunications and Network Communications Expert Witness Services</h2>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Telecommunications Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian provides expert witness services in telecommunications, including analysis of telecom systems, protocols, and patents. His expertise covers traditional and modern telecommunications technologies used in patent litigation and dispute resolution.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Network Communications Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>With extensive experience in network communications technologies and standards, Dr. Lavian serves as an expert witness in complex cases involving data transmission, network architectures, and communications protocols.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Computer Network Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian's expertise in computer networks encompasses networking hardware, software, protocols, and systems. He provides analysis and testimony on computer network technologies, architectures, and patent validity in litigation.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Internet Protocols Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>As an expert in Internet protocols including TCP/IP, DNS, BGP, and other fundamental protocols, Dr. Lavian provides testimony on protocol implementations, standards compliance, and patent claims related to Internet technologies.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Internet and Web Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian offers expert testimony on Internet and Web technologies, including web protocols, browsers, web services, and Internet applications. His analysis covers both technical implementation and patent infringement assessments.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Routing and Switching Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>With deep expertise in routing, switching, and network forwarding technologies, Dr. Lavian provides expert analysis on routing protocols, switch design, and network topology optimization in patent cases.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">VoIP Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian has extensive experience with Voice over IP (VoIP) technologies, including signaling protocols, codec standards, and network integration. He provides expert testimony on VoIP patent validity and infringement.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Mobile Wireless Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>As an expert in mobile and wireless technologies, Dr. Lavian provides testimony on cellular systems, wireless protocols, mobile networks, and related patent matters in litigation involving telecommunications companies.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Streaming Media Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian's expertise in streaming media includes audio and video streaming technologies, protocols, compression standards, and delivery networks. He provides analysis on streaming media patents in litigation contexts.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Network Systems Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>With comprehensive knowledge of network systems architecture, design, and implementation, Dr. Lavian serves as an expert witness on complex network systems patents and technical disputes in litigation.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">LAN/WAN Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian provides expert testimony on Local Area Networks (LANs) and Wide Area Networks (WANs), including network design, protocols, interconnection technologies, and related patent matters.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Cloud Computing Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>As an expert in cloud computing technologies, infrastructure, and architectures, Dr. Lavian provides analysis and testimony on cloud computing patents, systems, and technical issues in litigation.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Cellular Technology Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian's expertise in cellular technology covers multiple generations of cellular systems from 2G through 5G, including standards, protocols, and network architectures relevant to patent litigation.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Web Technologies and Applications Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>With extensive knowledge of web technologies, web applications, frameworks, and development practices, Dr. Lavian provides expert testimony on web-related patents and technical matters in litigation.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Internet Technology Patents Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian specializes in Internet technology patents, providing expert analysis on patent validity, infringement, claim construction, and technical feasibility of Internet-related inventions.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Underlay Networks and Protocols Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>As an expert in underlay network technologies and underlying network protocols, Dr. Lavian provides testimony on foundational network infrastructure, protocols, and patent matters in complex litigation.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2d3e6f;font-size:1.2rem;">Telecommunication and Network Management Expert Witness</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian provides expert testimony on telecommunications and network management systems, including management protocols, monitoring systems, and operational technologies used in modern networks.</p>

